			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A\r\n- Use ReCon command \"oe MT_Baptism\" and then \"goto -1259 2 466\". The cultists will appear and start their chant - that chant is a different AD though.\r\n- Attack one of the cultists. On the first general combat turn, all the cultists will say this chant simultaneously."
				},
