				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "During the Baptism of Blood at the Murder Tribunal, numerous cultists will appear in the background, ritualistically chanting while the ritual goes on. If we attack them though, they will start doing this chant instead, on the first general combat turn."
				}
